<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include("partials/head_css") %>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("partials/loader") %>

    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <main>

        <!--================= Banner section start =================-->
        <section class="vl-breadcrumb-bg p-relative z-index-1 fix pt-200 pb--70" style="background-image: url(/img/banner/vl-breadcrumb-bg.png);">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-30">
                        <div class="vl-breadcrumb">
                            <h1 class="vl-fs-60 vl-white">Blog Details</h1>
                            <div class="vl-breadcrumb-list">
                                <span><a href="/">Home</a></span>
                                <span class="dvir"><i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i></span>
                                <span><a href="/blog">Our Blog</a></span>
                                <span class="dvir"><i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i></span>
                                <span class="active"><a href="#">Blog Details</a></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-30">
                        <div class="vl-hero-img p-relative">
                            <div class="vl-hero-shape-4">
                                <div class="vl-shape-2">
                                    <img src="/img/icons/vl-emoji-4.2.svg" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="vl-shape-3">
                                    <img src="/img/icons/vl-emoji-4.3.svg" alt="">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="vl-breadcrumb-fan">
                                <img class="w-100" src="/img/icons/vl-fan-sm.svg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="vl-breadcrumb-img">
                                <img src="/img/banner/vl-breadcrumb-1.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!--================= Banner section End =================-->

        <!--================= Blog Details Start =================-->
        <section class="vl-service-deatil pt-100 pb-100">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <div class="vl-service-details">
                            <div class="vl-block-content mb-30">
                                <h2 class="vl-fs-36 vl-lineheight-42 vl-text-cmn-blck pb-20 m-0">Building Custom Mobile & Web SaaS Applications in Somalia</h2>
                                <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-18 vl-lineheight-28 m-0">In today's fast-evolving digital landscape, businesses and educational institutions across Somalia require tailored tech solutions built specifically for local needs. At Infinity Tech in Wadada Debka, we specialize in high-performance iOS and Android mobile app development, modern Node.js web platforms, and automated School SaaS systems.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="vl-service-details-larg-img fix br-8 mb-30">
                                <img class="w-100" src="/img/blog/somali-blog-1.jpg" alt="Building Custom Mobile & Web SaaS Applications">
                            </div>

                            <div class="vl-service-details-cat pt-24 pb-24 mb-30">
                                <div class="vl-service-details-cat-single vl-service-details-cat-single-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa-regular fa-user" style="color: #0D43FE;"></i></span>
                                    <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-16 vl-lineheight-16 m-0"><strong>Author:</strong> Abubakar Hashi</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="vl-service-details-cat-single vl-service-details-cat-single-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-days" style="color: #0D43FE;"></i></span>
                                    <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-16 vl-lineheight-16 m-0">23 July 2026</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="vl-service-details-cat-single vl-service-details-cat-single-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa-regular fa-folder" style="color: #0D43FE;"></i></span>
                                    <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-16 vl-lineheight-16 m-0">Mobile & Web Engineering</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="vl-block-content mb-30">
                                <h3 class="vl-fs-28 vl-lineheight-32 vl-text-cmn-blck pb-20 m-0">Why Native & Cross-Platform Mobile Apps Matter</h3>
                                <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-18 vl-lineheight-28 pb-20 m-0">Mobile connectivity is the primary digital doorway in East Africa. Developing seamless mobile applications with fast offline capability, intuitive user experiences, and multi-lingual support ensures your products reach every user effortlessly.</p>
                                <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-18 vl-lineheight-28 m-0">Our engineering approach prioritizes security, scalable API integrations, and ultra-fast loading speeds on mobile networks.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="vl-block-quote vl-gray-bg-4 br-8 mb-30 p-relative z-index-1 fix" style="border-left: 4px solid #0D43FE; padding: 24px;">
                                <p class="vl-text-para vl-fs-18 vl-lineheight-28 m-0"><em>“Technology is not just about writing code—it is about solving real local operational challenges and empowering Somali businesses and schools to scale effortlessly.”</em></p>
                                <strong class="pt-12 d-block" style="color: #0D43FE;">— Abubakar Hashi, Lead Software Architect</strong>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="vl-blog-tags mb-30">
                                        <h3 class="vl-fs-20 vl-lineheight-20 vl-text-cmn-blck m-0 mr-15">Tags:</h3>
                                        <div class="vl-blog-tag">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><span>#</span>MobileApp</a></li>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><span>#</span>WebDev</a></li>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><span>#</span>SchoolSaaS</a></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    <div class="vl-blog-share mb-30 fl-right">
                                        <h3 class="vl-fs-20 vl-lineheight-20 vl-text-cmn-blck m-0 mr-15">Share Article:</h3>
                                        <div class="vl-sidebar-social vl-sidebar-social-2">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i></a></li>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i></a></li>
                                                <li><a href="javascript:void(0);"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i></a></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!--================= Blog Details End =================-->

    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>

    <%- include("partials/progress_circle") %>

    <%- include("partials/footer_scripts") %>
</body>

</html>